<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>YourKitchen — B2B Sales Process & Attack Plan</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600;9..40,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --sage: #3D6B4F;
    --sage-mid: #6B9E7E;
    --sage-light: #EAF2ED;
    --cream: #FAFAF5;
    --forest: #1E2620;
    --amber: #C17F47;
    --amber-light: #F5EBDD;
    --stone: #6B7066;
    --border: #DDE8E0;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --serif: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    background: #EDEDE6;
    color: var(--forest);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    padding: 32px 16px 64px;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .header {
    background: var(--forest);
    border-radius: 18px 18px 0 0;
    padding: 44px 52px 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: -60px; top: -60px;
    width: 280px; height: 280px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(107,158,126,0.18), transparent 70%);
  }
  .header-eyebrow {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.42em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-mid);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .header-brand {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .header-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(250,250,245,0.65);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .header-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 22px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .header-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(107,158,126,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(107,158,126,0.35);
    color: #CDE3D5;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 6px 13px;
    border-radius: 30px;
  }

  /* ── SHEET ── */
  .sheet {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(30,38,32,0.14);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── SECTION WRAPPER ── */
  .section {
    padding: 44px 52px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.38em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--forest);
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  /* ── FLOWCHART ── */
  .flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .flow-stage {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .flow-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
  }

  .flow-node {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sage);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .flow-node.amber { background: var(--amber); }
  .flow-node.forest { background: var(--forest); }
  .flow-node.sage-mid { background: var(--sage-mid); }

  .flow-line {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 32px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .flow-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .flow-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .flow-label.amber { color: var(--amber); }
  .flow-label.forest { color: var(--forest); }

  .flow-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .flow-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .flow-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .action-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--sage);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 5px 11px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .action-chip.amber {
    background: var(--amber-light);
    border-color: rgba(193,127,71,0.25);
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .action-chip.forest {
    background: var(--forest);
    border-color: var(--forest);
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  /* Branch box */
  .branch-box {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .branch {
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
  }
  .branch.yes {
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .branch.no {
    background: var(--amber-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(193,127,71,0.22);
  }
  .branch-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .branch.yes .branch-label { color: var(--sage); }
  .branch.no .branch-label { color: var(--amber); }
  .branch p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── ATTACK PLAN GRID ── */
  .attack-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .attack-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .attack-card.priority {
    border-color: var(--sage);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sage);
  }

  .attack-week {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-mid);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .attack-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .attack-body {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.62;
  }

  .attack-target {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 4px 9px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  .goal-tag {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--forest);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  /* ── SCRIPT BOX ── */
  .script-box {
    background: var(--forest);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 26px 28px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .script-label {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-mid);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .script-line {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .script-line:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .script-tag {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-mid);
    width: 64px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .script-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(250,250,245,0.88);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── SEGMENT TABLE ── */
  .seg-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .seg-table th {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone);
    padding: 0 12px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--border);
  }
  .seg-table td {
    padding: 11px 12px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--stone);
  }
  .seg-table td:first-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--forest);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .seg-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .seg-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: rgba(234,242,237,0.3); }

  .channel-dot {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .ch-visit { background: var(--sage-light); color: var(--sage); }
  .ch-call { background: var(--amber-light); color: var(--amber); }
  .ch-email { background: #EEF0F8; color: #4A5080; }
  .ch-linkedin { background: #E8F1FB; color: #2D6FA8; }

  /* ── METRICS STRIP ── */
  .metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--border);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .metric {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 20px 22px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .metric-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sage);
    display: block;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .metric-label {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--stone);
    margin-top: 3px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    padding: 26px 52px 32px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .footer-brand {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--sage);
  }
  .footer-meta {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--stone);
  }

  /* ── PREMISE BOX ── */
  .premise-box {
    background: var(--forest);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .premise-label {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-mid);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .premise-statement {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sage-mid);
    padding-left: 18px;
  }
  .premise-sub {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: rgba(250,250,245,0.68);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── REVENUE GRID ── */
  .rev-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .rev-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 20px 18px;
  }
  .rev-card.highlight {
    border-color: var(--amber);
    background: var(--amber-light);
  }
  .rev-label {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--stone);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .rev-card.highlight .rev-label { color: var(--amber); }
  .rev-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sage);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: block;
  }
  .rev-card.highlight .rev-num { color: var(--amber); }
  .rev-body {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1.62;
  }

  /* ── OBJECTIONS ── */
  .obj-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .obj-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .obj-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 24px 0; }
  .obj-q {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--forest);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .obj-tag {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .obj-a {
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .obj-a-label {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .obj-a p { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--stone); line-height: 1.68; margin: 0; }
  .obj-a p strong { color: var(--forest); font-weight: 600; }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .section, .header, .footer { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
    .attack-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .branch-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .metrics { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .header-meta { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .rev-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media print {
    @page { size: Letter; margin: 0.4in; }
    body { background: #fff; padding: 0; }
    .page { max-width: 100%; }
    .header { border-radius: 0; }
    .sheet { border-radius: 0; box-shadow: none; }
    .flow-node, .script-box, .metrics .metric, .footer { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-eyebrow">YourKitchen LLC</div>
    <div class="header-brand">B2B Sales Process & Partner Attack Plan</div>
    <div class="header-title">From first contact to signed Kitchen Pool — every step mapped.</div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <div class="header-pill">🎯 100 Outreach Targets</div>
      <div class="header-pill">🏢 7 Partner Segments</div>
      <div class="header-pill">💼 Enterprise Kitchen Pool Model</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sheet">

    <!-- SECTION 1: FLOWCHART -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="eyebrow">Sales Process</div>
      <div class="section-title">From cold contact to contracted partner</div>
      <div class="section-sub">Every B2B conversation follows this path. The goal of each stage is only to earn the next one — not to close the deal prematurely.</div>

      <div class="flow">

        <!-- Stage 1 -->
        <div class="flow-stage">
          <div class="flow-left">
            <div class="flow-node">1</div>
            <div class="flow-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-content">
            <div class="flow-label">Identify</div>
            <div class="flow-title">Find the right person, not just the org</div>
            <div class="flow-body">Research who handles community partnerships, social work referrals, or client care coordination. This is never the front desk. It's the doula owner, the hospice social worker, the church benevolence pastor, the clinic care coordinator.</div>
            <div class="flow-actions">
              <span class="action-chip">🔍 LinkedIn search</span>
              <span class="action-chip">📞 Call to ask "who handles care partnerships?"</span>
              <span class="action-chip">🌐 Website staff page</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stage 2 -->
        <div class="flow-stage">
          <div class="flow-left">
            <div class="flow-node sage-mid">2</div>
            <div class="flow-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-content">
            <div class="flow-label">First Contact</div>
            <div class="flow-title">Lead with their world — not your product</div>
            <div class="flow-body">Make contact through the right channel for the segment. Open with a question about their clients, not a pitch about YK. The goal is one thing: a 15-minute conversation.</div>
            <div class="flow-actions">
              <span class="action-chip">🚪 In-person visit</span>
              <span class="action-chip amber">📧 Short 2-paragraph email</span>
              <span class="action-chip">💼 LinkedIn personal message</span>
              <span class="action-chip amber">📞 Warm phone call</span>
            </div>
            <div class="branch-box">
              <div class="branch yes">
                <div class="branch-label">✓ They respond</div>
                <p>Schedule the 15-minute intro call. Send a calendar link same day — don't let momentum die.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="branch no">
                <div class="branch-label">↻ No response</div>
                <p>Follow up once at 5 days with a different angle. If still nothing, move on — don't burn goodwill. Return in 60 days.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stage 3 -->
        <div class="flow-stage">
          <div class="flow-left">
            <div class="flow-node amber">3</div>
            <div class="flow-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-content">
            <div class="flow-label amber">Discovery Call — 15 min</div>
            <div class="flow-title">Ask more than you tell</div>
            <div class="flow-body">This is not a demo. Ask 3 questions, listen hard, connect what you heard to what YK does. Close by asking if a walkthrough would be useful.</div>
            <div class="script-box">
              <div class="script-label">Conversation Guide</div>
              <div class="script-line">
                <div class="script-tag">Open</div>
                <div class="script-text">"Do families you work with ever struggle to coordinate meals during [the recovery / grief / deployment / postpartum] period?"</div>
              </div>
              <div class="script-line">
                <div class="script-tag">Deepen</div>
                <div class="script-text">"What does that usually look like — is it friends asking how to help, or families just going without?"</div>
              </div>
              <div class="script-line">
                <div class="script-tag">Bridge</div>
                <div class="script-text">"That's exactly what YourKitchen solves. A family's village claims dates, picks a restaurant meal, and pays — the family just confirms by text. Nothing is charged until they say yes."</div>
              </div>
              <div class="script-line">
                <div class="script-tag">Ask</div>
                <div class="script-text">"Would it be helpful to see how it works? I can walk you through a live kitchen in about 20 minutes."</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stage 4 -->
        <div class="flow-stage">
          <div class="flow-left">
            <div class="flow-node">4</div>
            <div class="flow-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-content">
            <div class="flow-label">Demo — 20 min</div>
            <div class="flow-title">Show Danielle's kitchen. Make it real.</div>
            <div class="flow-body">Walk them through a live kitchen end to end. Show the coordinator page, the calendar claim, the SMS confirmation, the delivery. Then show the org dashboard concept — the Kitchen Pool, activation, expiration, and the one-click to serve a client.</div>
            <div class="flow-actions">
              <span class="action-chip">📱 Show live coordinator flow</span>
              <span class="action-chip">💬 Show SMS confirmation</span>
              <span class="action-chip amber">🏢 Show org pool dashboard concept</span>
              <span class="action-chip">📊 Show 90-day slot lifecycle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="branch-box">
              <div class="branch yes">
                <div class="branch-label">✓ Strong interest</div>
                <p>Propose the pilot: "Let me give you 2 trial slots for 30 days. Activate them for two real clients. Zero cost, no commitment."</p>
              </div>
              <div class="branch no">
                <div class="branch-label">◎ Hesitant</div>
                <p>Ask what's missing. Leave the one-pager. Follow up in 2 weeks with a relevant story or stat. Don't push — plant.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stage 5 -->
        <div class="flow-stage">
          <div class="flow-left">
            <div class="flow-node sage-mid">5</div>
            <div class="flow-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-content">
            <div class="flow-label">Pilot — 30 days</div>
            <div class="flow-title">Two real clients. You watch every order.</div>
