    <!-- SECTION 3: ATTACK PLAN -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="eyebrow">Attack Plan</div>
      <div class="section-title">100 outreach contacts — 8 week sprint</div>
      <div class="section-sub">Front-load your highest-conversion segments. Build momentum early so you have real pilot stories before you approach harder-to-reach orgs like hospitals and EAPs.</div>

      <div class="attack-grid">

        <div class="attack-card priority">
          <div class="goal-tag">Week 1–2</div>
          <div class="attack-week">Priority Segment · 25 contacts</div>
          <div class="attack-title">Doulas, Midwives & Postpartum Providers</div>
          <div class="attack-body">Highest emotional resonance. Solo practitioners who make referral decisions immediately. Show up in person with flyer + phone demo. You have a personal origin story that lands here.</div>
          <div class="attack-target">🎯 Goal: 3 pilots committed</div>
        </div>

        <div class="attack-card priority">
          <div class="goal-tag">Week 1–2</div>
          <div class="attack-week">Priority Segment · 15 contacts</div>
          <div class="attack-title">Faith Communities — Houston Area</div>
          <div class="attack-body">One pastor = hundreds of families. Start with churches that already run benevolence ministries or meal ministries. Ask for 15 minutes with the care pastor. Leave the flyer. Follow up with a demo link.</div>
          <div class="attack-target">🎯 Goal: 2 church champions</div>
        </div>

        <div class="attack-card">
          <div class="goal-tag">Week 3–4</div>
          <div class="attack-week">Core Segment · 20 contacts</div>
          <div class="attack-title">Hospice & Home Health Agencies</div>
          <div class="attack-body">Call first to identify the social work director. Visit with your one-pager. These orgs have more process but higher contract value and longer relationships. Plant now, close in week 6–8.</div>
          <div class="attack-target">🎯 Goal: 2 discovery calls booked</div>
        </div>

        <div class="attack-card">
          <div class="goal-tag">Week 3–4</div>
          <div class="attack-week">Core Segment · 15 contacts</div>
          <div class="attack-title">Funeral Homes</div>
          <div class="attack-body">Walk in. Ask for the owner or family services director. This segment is radically underserved and has zero competition. Your ask is simple: "Be the resource you give families for the weeks after." No contract needed to start.</div>
          <div class="attack-target">🎯 Goal: 5 referral agreements</div>
        </div>

        <div class="attack-card">
          <div class="goal-tag">Week 5–6</div>
          <div class="attack-week">Outreach Segment · 15 contacts</div>
          <div class="attack-title">Oncology Navigators & Hospital Social Work</div>
          <div class="attack-body">Email the department director with a 2-paragraph note. Include the live app link. Subject line: "A resource for families managing meals during treatment." Follow up once by phone. Getting on their referral list is the win here.</div>
          <div class="attack-target">🎯 Goal: 3 on referral list</div>
        </div>

