          <div class="attack-body">Email + flyer to FRG leaders and Blue Star Families chapter coordinators. Deployment spouse use case is distinct and underserved. If you know anyone connected to military communities in Texas, ask for a warm intro first.</div>
          <div class="attack-target">🎯 Goal: 2 org partnerships</div>
